./my-claw/sdp/prd-artist-plan-completion.md:21:| APC-007 | Implement a sound postcard sticker generator that captures current musical state, generates a haiku, and renders a waveform landscape for thermal printing. | SHOULD | T2 | - Reads current key, amplitude, and mood from state files<br/>- Generates a context-aware haiku (local LLM or template fallback)<br/>- Renders printable bitmap with waveform visualization and haiku text |
